                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-78-defend747 t17900526-78-punish381"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900526-78-person765">
                  JOHN
                   MARLBOROUGH
               <interp inst="t17900526-78-person765" type="surname" value="MARLBOROUGH"></interp>
