               GUILTY
            </rs>,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900526-78-punish383" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900526-78-punish383" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-78-defend752 t17900526-78-punish383"></join>
               Transported for fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900526-78-person766">
                  John
                   Marlborough
               <interp inst="t17900526-78-person766" type="surname" value="Marlborough"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900526-78-person766" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900526-78-person766" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was recommended to mercy by the jury, from motives of compassion, having a large family, and his wife laying in.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice ASHURST.</p>
